This:

> “AI may advise. AI may explain. AI may optimize. AI may correlate. AI may recommend. AI may NOT authoritatively govern.”

is absolutely the correct doctrine.

And more importantly:

## this is not marketing language

It is a systems architecture rule.

That distinction matters enormously.

